description: The king of Florince`s Otome, the Abyssal Green Jadeite (深淵の翡翠, Shin`en no Hisui). She plans to retire in order to marry. In My Otome Zwei, she appears in the baths with the other girls and confronts Shiho Huit, expressing her dislike for the girl. Her element is a whip.
name: Rosalie Claudel
